## Components

### Applications

- **Repo:** [drink-free-days-iaas](https://github.com/ukhsa-collaboration/dfd_cloudformation_iaas) – Django CMS mobile client.
- **Repo:** [drinkfree-days-nhs-login-backend](https://github.com/ukhsa-collaboration/drinkfree-days-nhs-login-backend) – FastAPI service that handles NHS login flows and syncs data. It also caches JWT tokens tokens in Redis.

### Infrastructure as Code (IaC)

- **Repo:** [drink-free-days-iac](https://github.com/ukhsa-collaboration/drink-free-days-iac) – Terraform code for the infrastructure.

